org.sbolstandard.core

Class SBOLFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sbolstandard.core.SBOLFactory
  • Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public class SBOLFactory
extends Object
    SBOL factory class that provides functionality to create SBOL objects and utility classes such as readers, writers, and validators.
    Author:
    Evren Sirin

    • Method Detail

      • read

        public static SBOLDocument read(InputStream in)
                         throws IOException,
                                SBOLValidationException
        Deprecated. 
        Creates a fresh SBOL document instance and populates its contents from the given XML source. The reader will perform validation automatically. The documents read by this reader are guaranteed to be valid so it is not necessary to perform validation. If the contents of the document is changed afterwards, validation will be needed.
        Throws:
        SBOLValidationException - if the contents of the document is not valid
        IOException

      • write

        public static void write(SBOLDocument doc,
                         OutputStream out)
                  throws IOException,
                         SBOLValidationException
        Deprecated. 
        Writes the contents of an SBOL document in XML format to the given output stream. The writer will perform validation automatically.
        Throws:
        SBOLValidationException - if the contents of the document is not valid
        IOException

      • createReader

        public static SBOLReader createReader()
        Deprecated. 
        Creates a new reader instance for reading from XML documents that will automatically perform validation and will refuse to load invalid documents.

      • createNoValidationReader

        public static SBOLReader createNoValidationReader()
        Deprecated. 
        Creates a new reader instance for writing SBOL documents as XML that will NOT perform validation. The documents read by this reader may not be written successfully if the writer performs validation.

      • createWriter

        public static SBOLWriter createWriter()
        Deprecated. 
        Creates a new writer instance for writing SBOL documents as XML that will automatically perform validation and will refuse to write invalid documents. WARNING: If validation fails while writing the contents of the document, the output may still contain partial serialization results that has been written before the error is discovered.

      • createNoValidationWriter

        public static SBOLWriter createNoValidationWriter()
        Deprecated. 
        Creates a new writer instance for writing SBOL documents as XML that will NOT perform validation. THe documents written by this writer may not be read successfully if the reader performs validation.
